113
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,480
Never get attached to them!

114
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,480
I just made a friend, that's all.

115
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,760
Like I said,

116
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,200
no feelings for them allowed.

117
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,640
Not even friends.

118
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:20,000
We have a special background.

119
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,600
They don't deserve us.

120
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:25,000
We don't need their shallow love.

121
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,760
Let go of those useless feelings.

122
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,240
